{"tid":2425203,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"（連登無人睇）小太郎一個人生活","createTime":"2021-02-27T07:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T08:19:34.000Z","uid":28170,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f7c527f7f65c14cae93b506a46dd2464fb6c53","tid":2425203,"uid":28170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T07:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uzLeKob.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuzLeKob.png&h=a5e0aea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲咩王道漫，轉生開掛睇到厭<br />\n<br />\n睇番呢啲日常漫好清泉<br />\n咁高質既漫畫連登竟然無人睇<br />\n<br />\n講一個五歲孤兒老豆比人拉左，老母死左，留底一筆保險金比佢過活<br />\n<br />\n故事環繞小太郎身邊既人展開，講解孤兒既角度既日常，主角同身邊既人點樣互相慰藉<br />\n<br />\n小太郎既故事好難想象到作者係咪都有過咁既經歷<br />\n<br />\n睇左百幾話<br />\n<br />\n最深刻真係百貨公司幫啲走失兒童<br />\n<br />\n果種天真同落寞，一頁就表達晒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人討論下"},{"pid":"997911f12edcab3e03601141c533d51aaa87e46b","tid":2425203,"uid":200529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T07:51:00.000Z","msg":"動漫台:主角冇開掛冇後宮唔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11565a1ef394680c12aeb718f221c921845e28e2","tid":2425203,"uid":28170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"997911f12edcab3e03601141c533d51aaa87e46b","tid":2425203,"uid":200529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T07:51:00.000Z","msg":"動漫台:主角冇開掛冇後宮唔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:19:34.000Z","msg":"本來睇咩喊既戲都無咩感覺<br />\n係呢套睇到眼濕濕<br />\n<br />\n百幾話都未交代晒佢父母<br />\n<br />\n係外人睇佢父母係衰人<br />\n<br />\n係小太郎心入面佢地都有好既一面"}]}